[OVERLAY] VimFu — :set wrap / nowrap
[SAY] Wrap controls whether long lines wrap to the next screen line or extend off the edge.
[SAY] By default, wrap is on. The long line wraps to multiple screen lines.
[SAY] Turn off wrapping.
[TYPE] ':set nowrap'

